body_html:
Can you give the outputs of

otool -L /usr/local/lib/python3.6/site-packages/caffe2/python/caffe2_pybind11_state.cpython-36m-darwin.so

echo $DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH
echo $PATH
echo $PYTHONPATH

python
# now in python run
import sys; sys.path

nm -A /usr/local/lib/* 2>/dev/null | grep -E '_PyCObject_Type'
# or if there's no output then try
nm -A /usr/local/lib/* 2>/dev/null | grep -E 'Object.*Type'
